":false,"myth":false,"baby":false,"eggs":["Water 3"],"flavor":[{"version":"ruby","text":"ARMALDO\u2019s tough armor makes all attacks bounce off. This POK\u00e9MON\u2019s two enormous claws can be freely extended or contracted. They have the power to punch right through a steel slab."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"ARMALDO is a POK\u00e9MON species that became extinct in prehistoric times. This POK\u00e9MON is said to have walked on its hind legs, which would have been more convenient for life on land."},{"version":"emerald","text":"ARMALDO usually lives on land. However, when it hunts for prey, it dives beneath the ocean. It swims around using its two large wings."},{"version":"firered","text":"Protected by a hard shell, its body is very sturdy. It skewers prey with its claws to feed."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Protected by a hard shell, its body is very sturdy. It skewers prey with its claws to feed."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Its enormous, retractable claws can cut through most anything. Its entire body is clad in sturdy plates."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its enormous, retractable claws can cut through most anything. Its entire body is clad in sturdy plates."},{"version":"black","text":"It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor."},{"version":"white","text":"It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor."},{"version":"x","text":"Its enormous, retractable claws can cut throug